docs/build_story_run.log:938:Codex also accelerated review cycles. We inspected real mobile screenshots, changed recall from a burdensome full-sentence requirement to a word-focused cloze with an optional AI sentence challenge, made the free diagnostic the first guest experience, and verified the production path with automated and live checks.
